Product Requirement Document: AI Mockup Generator
Objective
To provide a self-service tool for the Ergospace design and marketing teams to generate high-quality product lifestyle images without manual rendering.

User Stories
As a Designer, I want to upload a raw product mockup and choose an office scene so I can see the product in context instantly.

As a Team Lead, I want to see a gallery of all generated images so we can maintain brand consistency across the marketplace.

As a Product Manager, I want to control the output size (Square, Banner, Portrait) to ensure images fit various web and social modules.

Success Metrics
Time-to-Asset: Reduce from 14 days to <60 seconds.

User Adoption: 100% of marketplace lifestyle imagery generated via internal AI tools.
